public static InetAddress getLocalAddress() {
        if (LOCAL_ADDRESS != null)
            return LOCAL_ADDRESS;
        InetAddress localAddress = getLocalAddress0();
        LOCAL_ADDRESS = localAddress;
        return localAddress;
    }
```

Do not use the `deprecated AnnotationBean` in your project.
Use the new annotation implementation instead, currently, you can refer [here](https://github.com/mercyblitz/blogs/blob/master/java/dubbo/Dubbo-New-Programming-Model.md
) and [the docs](http://dubbo.io/books/dubbo-user-book/configuration/annotation.html).
